INSERT INTO `db_article` VALUES (1,'asdf','aa4151da-fbb9-11ef-8c68-2d8a2d43c71f','\"/pic/uploads/20250307223051920-zelensky-2.webp\"','<p>qwerasdf</p>',7,3,'3',2,0,170,1,'2025-03-07 22:31:02','2025-05-27 16:27:18'),(2,'The difficult choices facing Ukraine\'s Zelensky','aa4151da-fbb9-11ef-8c68-2d8a2d43c71f','\"/pic/randcover//pic4.jpg\"','<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Ukraine&#39;s Volodymyr Zelensky is in a bind.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">After last Friday&#39;s disastrous meeting in the Oval Office, it seems nothing that he says goes down well with President Donald Trump. And now the US has suspended aid to Ukraine, his options are looking increasingly thin.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Even a former close Republican ally in the US, Senator Lindsey Graham, has turned on him, suggesting &quot;he either needs to resign and send somebody over that we can do business with, or he needs to change&quot;.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">What kind of change might that be - or should he resign if that&#39;s the price of US support?</p><h2 class=\"sc-518485e5-0 DkKTF\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 500; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 32px; line-height: 36px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.32px;\">Should he apologise to Trump?</h2><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">This option seems Zelensky&#39;s most likely way out and Ukraine&#39;s prime minister now says Kyiv is open to talks on signing a minerals deal with the US.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Trump told Zelensky point-blank on Friday he was not in a very good position: &quot;You don&#39;t have the cards right now - with us you start having cards.&quot;</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Zelensky had been ready to sign-off on the minerals deal with Trump on Friday before he was told to leave the White House.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">That particular card appears to have remained on the table, and on Monday night Zelensky&#39;s chief aide Andriy Yermak said he was working on it with Republican Congressman Brian Fitzpatrick and the deal was &quot;crucial for both our countries&quot;.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">But clearly the Trump administration is holding out for more.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Zelensky cannot afford to be humbled into an abject apology. After three years of Russian bombardment, Ukrainians are not in the mood for capitulation.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">But he would have to find a form of words sufficient to appease Trump.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">He might also have to accept a ceasefire on Trump&#39;s terms, even if he still believes peace is &quot;very, very far away&quot;.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Would the deal mean a resumption of aid and to what extent? Certainly that&#39;s a priority for Kyiv.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The head of parliament&#39;s foreign affairs committee, Oleksandr Merezhko, says suspending US aid is dangerous for Ukraine&#39;s ability to defend its own civilians.</p><h2 class=\"sc-518485e5-0 DkKTF\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 500; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 32px; line-height: 36px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.32px;\">Is resignation an option?</h2><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Falling on his sword is not something Zelensky will or can consider.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Trump has called him both unelected and a dictator, echoing Vladimir Putin&#39;s Russian propaganda narrative since the start of the war.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Zelensky said on Sunday night it seemed &quot;a bit undemocratic&quot; for Ukrainians to be told who should be their president.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">He is after all Ukraine&#39;s elected leader, and although his term was meant to end last year, he remains president under martial law, which came into place precisely because of Putin&#39;s Russian invasion.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">It would be a great result for Putin, who has sought to replace Zelensky since the start of the war and will not even talk directly to him &quot;because of his illegitimacy&quot;.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">But the only way Zelensky would consider it would be in exchange for Nato membership for Ukraine, and Trump has said he should forget about that.</p><ul class=\"sc-5c9c90b0-0 ggNdZQ list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); flex-direction: column; display: flex; gap: 12px; letter-spacing: -0.36px;\"><li><p><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/c981p3dxnent\" class=\"sc-c9299ecf-0 kNHAVz\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\">Follow live: Ukraine&#39;s PM says Kyiv determined to continue co-operation with US</a></p></li><li><p><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cwydq82e7r1o\" class=\"sc-c9299ecf-0 kNHAVz\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\">Ukraine&#39;s shock over US military aid pause</a></p></li><li><p><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/ce8yz5dk82wo\" class=\"sc-c9299ecf-0 kNHAVz\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\">Analysis: What the pause in aid could mean for Ukraine</a></p></li><li><p><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/videos/ckg84kpw5jwo\" class=\"sc-c9299ecf-0 kNHAVz\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\">BBC Verify: Can Europe fill the gap?</a></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"sc-518485e5-0 DkKTF\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 500; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 32px; line-height: 36px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.32px;\">Could he rely on Ukraine itself and Europe instead?</h2><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Several Ukrainian figures made clear on Tuesday they would hold out for as long as necessary without US aid, but some reports suggest the US pause has halted critically important air defence missiles and artillery.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Ukrainian MP Fedir Venislavskyi told local media that they could last about six months, but only the US could provide them with air defence systems and long-range multiple rocket systems.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Prime Minister Denys Shmyhal says Ukraine is already producing about a third of the weapons it needs, and its goal was 50%.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">So could Zelensky rely on European allies instead?</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">European nations have collectively paid out substantially more than the US in aid to Ukraine, and the head of the European Union&#39;s executive Commission, Ursula von der Leyen, has announced plans to beef up Europe&#39;s defence capability.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">She is proposing up to â‚¬800bn in defence funding - some of which would also go to helping Ukraine.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">But the EU and UK are adamant that US security guarantees are vital in the event of a ceasefire, even if in Sir Keir Starmer&#39;s words &quot;it is right that Europe do the heavy lifting&quot;.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Denis Shmyhal himself describes concrete US guarantees as &quot;existentially important&quot; for Ukraine and the entire continent.</p><p><br/></p>',10,1,'19',2,0,9,1,'2025-03-07 22:36:53','2025-05-27 00:05:58'),(3,'Trump says Ukraine \'more difficult\' to deal with than Russia','946e251c-fbf1-11ef-8c68-2d8a2d43c71f','\"/pic/uploads/20250308030740568-1200x1200bf-60.jpg\"','<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">US President Donald Trump has said he is finding it &quot;more difficult, frankly, to deal with Ukraine&quot; than Russia in attempts to broker peace between the two nations.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">The US is &quot;doing very well with Russia&quot;, and &quot;it may be easier dealing with&quot; Moscow than Kyiv, Trump told reporters in the Oval Office on Friday.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Hours earlier, Trump had said he was &quot;strongly considering&quot; large-scale sanctions and tariffs on Russia until a ceasefire with Ukraine was reached.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Meanwhile, the US has temporarily suspended Ukraine&#39;s access to some satellite imagery, space technology company Maxar told BBC Verify, after Trump had already paused military aid to the country.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">It comes exactly one week after an&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/c9dejydynngo\" class=\"sc-c9299ecf-0 beIoQm\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 26px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); text-decoration-line: underline; letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">extraordinary White House exchange</a>, in which Trump berated Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky for being &quot;disrespectful&quot; to the US.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">That public dressing-down was followed this week by Trump pausing all&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/ce8yz5dk82wo\" class=\"sc-c9299ecf-0 beIoQm\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 26px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); text-decoration-line: underline; letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">US military aid</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cn52k5n5w24o\" class=\"sc-c9299ecf-0 beIoQm\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 26px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); text-decoration-line: underline; letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">intelligence-sharing with Kyiv</a>.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Russia then conducted a large-scale missile and drone attack on Ukraine&#39;s energy infrastructure on Thursday night.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Trump&#39;s&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/c36wkpy3497o\" class=\"sc-c9299ecf-0 beIoQm\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 26px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); text-decoration-line: underline; letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">threat of further sanctions</a>&nbsp;on the already heavily sanctioned Russia was apparently in response to this attack. He said he was considering new tariffs because &quot;Russia is absolutely &#39;pounding&#39; Ukraine on the battlefield right now&quot;.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">But within hours, Trump said Russian President Vladimir Putin was acting as anyone else would.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">&quot;I think he&#39;s hitting them [Ukraine] harder than he&#39;s been hitting them,&quot; Trump said. &quot;And I think probably anyone in that position would be doing that right now.&quot;</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">He added that he believes Putin wants to end the war but he cannot say the same of Ukraine.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">&quot;I want to know they [Ukraine] want to settle and I don&#39;t know they want to settle,&quot; Trump said, when asked why he had cut off aid to Kyiv.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Trump&#39;s direct diplomacy with Putin stunned Nato allies, because the West has shunned contacts with Moscow since Russia&#39;s February 2022 full-scale invasion of Ukraine.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Despite Trump&#39;s row with Zelensky, the tone from his foreign policy team in the last two days has sounded more conciliatory towards Ukraine, after its arm-wrenching in the form of cutting off military and intelligence support.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The Americans want Zelensky to sign a deal that would give them a major stake in Ukrainian minerals, and for him to agree to a quick truce with Moscow.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Zelensky has been pushing for firm security guarantees for Kyiv, to be agreed as part of the deal. Speaking on Friday, Trump said such a security guarantee could be discussed later and would be the &quot;easy part&quot;.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Meanwhile, space technology company Maxar told BBC Verify on Friday that the US had temporarily suspended Ukrainian access to some high quality imagery from US satellites.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Satellite imagery is an important tool during a war as it allows armies to gather intelligence on their rivals.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Maxar, a US-based company, has contracts to provide satellite imagery to various governments and companies.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">One of those is the Global Enhanced GEOINT Deliver (GEGD) program, which gives users access to high quality imagery collected by the US government.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">&quot;The US government has decided to temporarily suspend Ukrainian accounts in GEGD,&quot; Maxar told the BBC. &quot;Each customer makes their own decisions on how they use and share that data.&quot;</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency, part of the US Department of Defense, confirmed the suspension was &quot;in accordance with the administration&#39;s directive on support to Ukraine&quot;.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Next week, Trump&#39;s senior officials will travel to Saudi Arabia to meet Zelensky&#39;s team amid growing pressure for him to sign up to Trump&#39;s demands.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Ukraine&#39;s president has said he&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cly2dz0qgxlo\" class=\"sc-c9299ecf-0 beIoQm\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 26px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); text-decoration-line: underline; letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">hopes the talks will be &quot;meaningful&quot;</a>. On Friday, he said his country was &quot;ready for peace as soon as possible&quot; and had proposed &quot;concrete steps&quot; to achieve it.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">&quot;Every day, new Russian strikes and reality itself prove that it is Russia that must be forced to peace,&quot; he added.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Zelensky has expressed regret in the days since his public clash with Trump and worked to mend relations with the US.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">On Thursday, US special envoy Steve Witkoff said Trump had received a letter from Zelensky that included an &quot;apology&quot; and &quot;sense of gratitude&quot;.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">&quot;Hopefully, we get things back on track with the Ukrainians, and everything resumes,&quot; Witkoff said.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">UK officials have said around 20 countries are interested in joining a&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/c2017v5ngxpo\" class=\"sc-c9299ecf-0 beIoQm\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 26px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); text-decoration-line: underline; letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">&quot;coalition of the willing&quot; to help Ukraine</a>, as European leaders forge ahead with plans for much bigger military expenditure.</p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Fighting on the ground in Ukraine continued on Friday, with five people killed by Russian troops in the Donetsk region, according to local authorities.</p><p><br/></p>',8,1,'49,90,25',0,0,23,1,'2025-03-08 03:08:13','2025-03-09 18:31:21'),(4,'1111','aa4151da-fbb9-11ef-8c68-2d8a2d43c71f','\"/pic/randcover//pic1.